Lowland primary forests, montane forests, secondary forests, and gardens from sea level up to elevations of ¢. 
<quantity id="4CFC9B09FFFAF6148B8E3C30FD5BF7D6" box="[656,766,2092,2125]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1" pageId="62" pageNumber="120" unit="m" value="1100.0">1100 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
